description:
This is all of ORIGINAL Leisure Suit Larry games. Leisure Suit Larry I, Leisure Suit Larry II, Leisure Suit Larry III, Leisure Suit Larry V, Leisure Suit Larry VI, and Sopftporn Adventure. 

Just mount the image on a virtual drive and open the file and either run the install from there or copy the files to your HDD and run the .exe no hack or crack needed.

You will need DOSbox to play it though which you can find the latest version here:
 &lt;a href=&quot;
http://www.dosbox.com/download.php?main=1&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow&quot; target=&quot;_NEW&quot;&gt;
http://www.dosbox.com/download.php?main=1&lt;/a&gt;

